ARCTIC.
CANADA-NORTH COAST.
1. 18 FOOT M/V, BURGUNDY HULL, TWO PERSONS ON BOARD,
   OVERDUE SPENCE BAY (69-32.2N 093-31.6W)
   TO GJOA HAVEN (68-37.5N 095-52.5W). LAST KNOWN
   POSITION VICINITY DUNDAS ISLAND (69-18.0N 094-31.0W)
   AT 201800Z SEP. VESSELS IN VICINITY REQUESTED
   TO KEEP A SHARP LOOKOUT, ASSIST IF POSSIBLE.
   REPORTS TO ANY COASTAL RADIO STATION.
2. CANCEL HYDROARC 180/13.
